Show HN: Castled – Marketing tool built on cloud data warehouses like Snowflake
text:
Castled is a marketing automation platform built on data warehouses like Snowflake, BigQuery, Redshift, and Postgres. Castled allows you to directly use the user data in Snowflake and target them across channels like Email, Sms, WhatsApp, push, and In-app - without having to copy the data to another tool.

We would love you to try it out and give us your feedback. We have created a demo database and put some dummy data there so you can try us out without any hassles.

Acquisition Opportunity: Innovative PKM Tool with 2.3k Users and 600k Bookmarks
text:
Hello,
I am the founder of TweepsBook - a consumer SaaS product, a PKM tool that aggregates all the bookmarks from popular apps like Reddit, Twitter, Pinterest, and more. Our users can also add custom links and scrape all the data of their bookmarks for a canvas layer to take and share notes. Imagine if Notion, Miro, and Pocket had a baby; that's our product.
We are proud to have won the official Twitter hackathon, and our launch on Product Hunt was a huge success, landing us at #4 on launch day. With more than 2.3k users and over 600k bookmarks, our product is growing, and we are now seeking acquisition offers.
We are open to offers of $5k or higher and would love to hear from potential acquirers who see value in our product and would like to take it to the next level. If you or anyone you know is interested, please contact me directly.
Link to our pitch deck: https://l.slipbox.it/deck
Thank you for your time and consideration!
